            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to control the game by countering opponents' spells, disrupting their plans with discard spells, and removing threats from the board with removal spells. Tasigur, the Golden Fang is used as the commander to utilize its ability to delve cards from the graveyard, providing card advantage and flexibility in casting spells. The deck includes a variety of counterspells, removal spells, and card draw spells to maintain control of the game and outvalue the opponent. The mana base is carefully constructed to ensure the deck has access to the necessary colors of mana to cast its spells efficiently. Overall, the deck aims to outmaneuver opponents through careful resource management and strategic decision-making."
